Titolo: FAR: Lone Sails

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: FAR: Lone Sails is an exploration adventure video game developed by the Swiss development company Okomotive. The game was released on Microsoft Windows and macOS on 17 May 2018, with Xbox One and PlayStation 4 versions released in April 2019, and the Nintendo Switch version on 18 August 2019. It was released in Japan on January 23, 2020.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: 83
